title: Episode 137: Daniel Cates "Jungleman" - The World's Best Poker Player
description:
Show Notes:

How Dan got into poker... (03:00)
How long it took him to build a million dollar bank roll... (04:30)
Dan explains the lifestyle of a rich young poker player… (08:00)
What happened on Black Friday... (10:45)
A hilarious story about being denied entry into Canada... (11:20)
Should you use a math based approach to dating like you would for poker? (13:30)
Is it helpful being young and rich with women or do you run into many gold diggers? (14:45) 
How celebrity status affect your success with women? (16:45)
What is the international party circuit? (18:50)
How you should invest your money at a young age when you start making big bucks? (21:00) 
Is becoming a star poker player as easy now as it was when Dan originally rose to fame? (24:00)
What advice Dan would give to young aspiring poker players... (25:30)
How Dan ended up playing the role of porn star in the middle of a party... (32:00)
How jungleman shocked the poker world for the second time... (34:00) 
Dan's experience living the Playboy lifestyle that no one ever talks about... (35:00) 
How Dan will approach his dating life going forward... (37:00)
The worlds most exclusive dating app called... (40:00)
Jungleman’s plan to break into Hollywood... (43:00)
What is the future of Jungleman in poker... (50:00)

channel_info.description:
I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.
